'''埃爾金'''（{{lang|en|'''Elgin'''}}）為[[美国|美国]][[堪薩斯州|堪薩斯州]][[學托擴縣_(堪薩斯州)|學托擴縣]]轄下的城市，鄰近堪薩斯州－[[奧克拉荷馬州|奧克拉荷馬州]][[边界|边界]]。根據[[2010年美國人口普查|2010年美國人口普查]]，此城市人口有89人<ref name="Census2010">{{cite web|title=2010 City Population and Housing Occupancy Status|url=http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|publisher=U.S. Census Bureau|accessdate=November 3, 2011|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218203744/http://factfinder2.census.gov/faces/tableservices/jsf/pages/productview.xhtml?pid=DEC_10_PL_GCTPL2.ST13&prodType=table|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==歷史==
埃爾金設立於1869年<ref>{{cite book | url=http://books.google.com/books?id=o8X5krq3fP8C&pg=PA572#v=onepage&q&f=false | title=Kansas: A Cyclopedia of State History, Embracing Events, Institutions, Industries, Counties, Cities, Towns, Prominent Persons, Etc. | publisher=Standard Publishing Company | author=Blackmar, Frank Wilson | year=1912 | pages=572}}</ref>。

此城市內的郵政局已於1976年裁撤<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CQ |title=Kansas Post Offices, 1828-1961 (archived) |publisher=Kansas Historical Society |accessdate=6 June 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009134430/http://www.kshs.org/geog/geog_postoffices/search/county:CQ |archivedate=2013-10-09 }}</ref>。

==地理==
埃爾金坐落於北緯37度0分6秒、西經96度16分51秒（亦可表示為37.001608, -96.280703）處<ref name="GR1">{{cite web|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2011-04-23|date=2011-02-12|title=US Gazetteer files: 2010, 2000, and 1990|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060720110047/http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/gazette.html|archive-date=2006-07-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。根據[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]的資料，此城市總面積為{{convert|0.52|sqkm|sqmi|2}}，全境皆為陸地<ref name ="Gazetteer files">{{cite web|title=US Gazetteer files 2010|url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|publisher=[[美国人口调查局|美国人口调查局]]|accessdate=2012-07-06|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/699nOulzi?url=http://www.census.gov/geo/www/gazetteer/files/Gaz_places_national.txt|archive-date=2012-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

